# ── CS of Doom — environment ──────────────────────────────────────────────
# Anthropic API key for the AI tutor + free-text answer grading.
# Used ONLY in server route handlers (app/api/*). Never shipped to the client.
# Create one at https://console.anthropic.com/  •  do NOT commit a real key.
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=

# Optional model overrides. Leave blank to use the app's built-in defaults
# (a Sonnet-class model for the conversational tutor, a Haiku-class model for
# cheap inline grading). The app resolves current model strings at runtime.
# ANTHROPIC_TUTOR_MODEL=
# ANTHROPIC_GRADER_MODEL=
